# Supported formats:
# 1. Full format: user@hostname:/path/to/source/file
# 2. Short format: @hostname:/path/to/source/file (requires --user option)

# Example entries with full format:
user@192.168.1.10:/var/log/application.log
admin@example.com:/home/admin/config.txt
root@10.0.0.5:/etc/nginx/nginx.conf

# Example entries with short format (use with --user option):
@web1.example.com:/var/log/nginx/access.log
@web2.example.com:/var/log/nginx/error.log
@db.example.com:/var/lib/mysql/mysql.log